      <title>参议员说，中国必须在美国贸易谈判之前修复芬太尼流。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-must-fix-fentanyl-flow-before-us-trade-talks-senator-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国参议员在与中国顶级官员会议之后说，北京需要采取行动，以阻止芬太尼前体向美国的流动，然后再进行贸易的进一步交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-must-fix-fentanyl-flow-before-us-trade-talks-senator-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 14:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安最高对手的逮捕对土耳其意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/what-arrest-of-erdogan-s-top-rival-means-for-turkey-quicktake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其法院将总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）判处最杰出的竞争对手，在周日因腐败指控逮捕了他，批评者说这是对民主的重大打击。伊斯坦布尔市长Ekrem Imamoglu准备宣布在2028年的总统投票中宣布自己的候选人资格，现在已从选举网格中删除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/what-arrest-of-erdogan-s-top-rival-means-for-turkey-quicktake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 13:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非被驱逐的美国大使说，他没有“不后悔”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/south-africa-s-expelled-us-ambassador-says-he-has-no-regrets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非大使从美国开除，回到了他的祖国，称他对导致他被告知离开的评论“不后悔”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/south-africa-s-expelled-us-ambassador-says-he-has-no-regrets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 13:09:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着抗议活动的增长，内塔尼亚胡的内阁开始驱逐法律局长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/netanyahu-s-cabinet-starts-to-oust-legal-chief-as-protests-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）的内阁周日迈出了第一步，朝着驳回总检察长的最新尝试，以减少对政府行动的司法监督。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/netanyahu-s-cabinet-starts-to-oust-legal-chief-as-protests-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 13:02:12 GMT</pubDate>
